text: Vrána (feminine Vránová) is a Czech surname (meaning "crow"), it may refer to: * Alena Vránová (born 1932), Czech actress * Jakub Vrána (born 1996), Czech ice hockey player * Josef Vrana, Czech Roman Catholic bishop * Pavel Vrána (born 1985), Czech footballer * Petr Vrána (born 1985, Czech ice hockey player * Vlasta Vrána (born 1950), Norway-Canadian actor Category:Czech-language surnames
title: Vrána
